articles.title: Liverpool FC player Diogo Jota killed in car crash in Spain, police say
articles.description: Liverpool F.C. soccer player Diogo Jota was reportedly killed in a car crash in Spain along with his brother [4, 5].

articles.title: Sean 'Diddy' Combs to remain detained ahead of sentencing
articles.description: Sean "Diddy" Combs was found guilty of two prostitution-related charges but acquitted of sex trafficking and racketeering charges [4].

articles.title: House Republicans are pushing Trump's big bill to the brink of passage
articles.description: House Republicans are ready to vote on President Donald Trump's $4.5 trillion tax breaks and spending cuts bill early Thursday [1, 3].
